        About Me: 
        </h2>
        <a class='word-break: break-all ' >Teach Jenn Tech is my personal platform where I dive into all things tech, from databases to JavaScript, TypeScript, and Python. I host livestreams and create educational content that breaks down these topics in a fun, approachable way. My goal is to help those who want to become developers or want to break into tech, not only understand but really adopt and enjoy the tools they’re working with. It’s all about making technology more human and building that sense of connection with the community.</a>
